    "Among the many topics he covered in his teaching, museology deserves to be singled out.": [],
    "He strongly promoted contemporary art, which in 1969 became a separate section of the art history curriculum.": [],
    "His career as a museum person began in 1959, as curator of the Brussels Royal Museums of Fine Arts.": [],
